# Trivy CVE allowlist for the container image.
#
# Format: one CVE ID per line (e.g. CVE-2024-12345). Blank lines and lines
# starting with "#" are ignored. Prefer fixing vulnerabilities to silencing
# them — only add entries here for CVEs you've explicitly triaged and decided
# to accept, and include a brief justification above the entry.
#
# Example:
#   # CVE-2024-9999: no exploit path in our use; upstream fix tracked in
#   # https://github.com/upstream/repo/issues/NNN — revisit 2026-07-01.
#   CVE-2024-9999
